 INTRODUCTION TO VIB


    You have heard a lot about Amiga viruses,  but you have newer seen 
    one of these nasty ones. 

    Your  Amiga have sometime a strange behavior or maybe some of your 
    floppy-disks or maybe ....you harddisk suddenly don't work correct 
    like before. WHAT'S IS HAPPENED?.......

    Have you ever had the same problem ???
    If YES,.... then read the below text.
    If NO, .....then you`re very lucky.......


    Virus  Information Base (VIB) is a exactly what the title says.  A
    database  from  where you can get information of vira of any type.
    Perhaps  you  have  wanted  to  know how a  certain virus hides in
    memory  or  you might be seeking information on a virus which have
    trashed your BBS or harddisk.  

    VIB  have  very  anvanced  search  functions and contains a lot of 
    grabbed IFF pictures of real Amiga viruses. The virus pictures are
    grabbed  from  infected  Amigas, and you will see these nasty ones 
    JUST .......as your own Amiga have been infected. 

    Futher  more you will find some few animated virus demos in VIB to 
    demonstrate  a  real virus infection of these viruses, (Please see
    the Amiga Knights, BGS9 and the Terrorists viuses!)
    
@Endnode

